      "bookSlug": "galatians",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Galatians 3:25",
      "text": "ܟܕ ܐܬܬ ܕܝܢ ܗܝܡܢܘܬܐ ܠܐ ܗܘܝܢ ܬܚܝܬ ܬܪܐܐ ܀",
